# AI Blog Generator using Make.com + OpenAI

## 🎥 Demo
[https://youtu.be/J-kY6meQJzc]

## ❓ Problem
Writing blogs manually takes time and effort.

## 💡 Solution
Built an automated system that generates blog content using AI.

## ⚙️ Workflow
1. Input topic
2. Trigger Make.com automation
3. Send request to OpenAI API
4. Receive generated blog content

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Make.com (automation)
- OpenAI API

## 📊 Use Cases
- SEO blog writing
- Content automation
- Marketing systems

## 🚀 Key Learning
Combining AI with automation creates powerful scalable systems.

